\c 19
\s Ukukhululwa kwelizwe lakoJuda
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi lapho inkosi uHezekhiya isizwile, yadabula izigqoko zayo\x + 18.37.\x*, yazembesa ngesaka\x + 1 Kho. 20.31.\x*, yangena endlini yeN\nd kosi\x + 19.14. Hlab. 73.16,17. 1 Kho. 8.29,30.\x*\nd*.
\v 2 Yasithuma uEliyakhimi owayephezu kwendlu, loShebina umabhalane, labadala babapristi, bembeswe ngamasaka\x + 1 Kho. 20.31.\x* kuIsaya umprofethi indodana kaAmozi\x + 2 Lan. 32.20.\x*.
\v 3 Basebesithi kuye: Utsho njalo uHezekhiya: Lolusuku lusuku lohlupho lolokusolwa lolokweyiswa; ngoba abantwana sebefikile emlonyeni wesizalo, kanti kakulamandla okubeletha.
\v 4 Mhlawumbe iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho izakuzwa wonke amazwi kaRabi-Shake\x + 2 Sam. 16.12.\x*, inkosi yeAsiriya inkosi yakhe eyamthumayo, ukuthi aklolodele uNkulunkulu ophilayo\x + 19.16. 18.35. 1 Sam. 17.26.\x*; njalo izasola amazwi\x + Hlab. 50.21.\x* iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ewezwileyo\x + Nani 12.2. 1 Sam. 7.9.\x*: Ngakho phakamiselani insali etholakeleyo umkhuleko\x + 17.6. Isa. 1.9.\x*.
\v 5 Izinceku zenkosi uHezekhiya zasezifika kuIsaya.
\v 6 UIsaya wasesithi kuzo: Lizakutsho njalo enkosini yenu: Utsho njalo uJehova: Ungesabi amazwi owezwileyo inceku zenkosi yeAsiriya ezingithuke ngawo\x + 18.17,28. 2 Sam. 9.9.\x*.
\v 7 Khangela, ngizafaka\x + 19.35,36,37.\x* umoya kuyo\x + Jer. 51.1. Isa. 37.7.\x*, njalo izakuzwa ihungahunga, ibuyele elizweni layo; ngizayenza ukuthi iwe ngenkemba elizweni layo\x + 19.9. 7.6.\x*.
\p
\v 8 URabi-Shake wasebuyela, wafica inkosi yeAsiriya isilwa imelene leLibhina\x + Josh. 10.29.\x*; ngoba wayezwile ukuthi isisukile eLakishi\x + 18.14.\x*.
\v 9 Kwathi isizwa ngoTirihaka\x + 1 Sam. 23.27.\x* inkosi yeEthiyophiya\x + Isa. 11.11. 18.1. 20.3-5. 43.3. 45.14. Gen. 10.6.\x* kuthiwa: Khangela, uphumile uku\add ya\add*kulwa emelene lawe, yabuya yathuma izithunywa kuHezekhiya, isithi:
\v 10 Lizakhuluma kanje kuHezekhiya inkosi yakoJuda, lithi: UNkulunkulu wakho omthembileyo\x + 18.5.\x* kangakukhohlisi esithi: IJerusalema kayiyikunikelwa esandleni senkosi yeAsiriya\x + 18.29,30.\x*.
\v 11 Khangela, wena usuzwile ukuthi amakhosi eAsiriya enzeni kuwo wonke amazwe, ngokuwatshabalalisa. Wena-ke uzakhululwa yini?
\v 12 Onkulunkulu bezizwe bazikhululile yini, obaba abazichithayo\x + 18.33.\x*, iGozani\x + 17.6.\x* leHarani\x + Hez. 27.23. Amos 1.5.\x*\x + Gen. 11.31. 27.43.\x* leRezefi labantwana bakaEdeni\x + Hez. 27.23. Amos 1.5.\x* ababeseTelasari\x + Isa. 37.12.\x*?
\v 13 Ingaphi inkosi yeHamathi\x + 18.34.\x*, lenkosi yeArpadi\x + Isa. 37.13.\x*, lenkosi yomuzi weSefavayimi, iHena, leIva?
\p
\v 14 UHezekhiya waseyemukela incwadi esandleni sezithunywa, wayibala, wasesenyukela endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*, uHezekhiya wayichaya phambi kweN\nd kosi\x + 19.9. 2 Lan. 32.17.\x*\nd*.
\v 15 UHezekhiya wasekhuleka phambi kweN\nd kosi\x + 2 Lan. 32.20.\x*\nd*, wathi: N\nd kosi\nd*, Nkulunkulu kaIsrayeli, ohlala \add phakathi\add* \w kwamakherubhi\w**\x + Eks. 25.22.\x*, wena unguNkulunkulu, wena wedwa, wayo yonke imibuso yomhlaba; wena wenze amazulu lomhlaba\x + 19.19. 1 Kho. 18.39. Neh. 9.6. Jer. 10.10,12. Hlab. 86.10.\x*.
\v 16 N\nd kosi\nd*, thoba indlebe yakho, uzwe\x + Hlab. 31.2. 71.2. Dan. 9.18.\x*, N\nd kosi\nd*, vula amehlo akho, ubone\x + Dan. 9.18. 2 Lan. 6.40.\x*; uzwe amazwi kaSenakheribi amthume ngawo ukuklolodela uNkulunkulu ophilayo\x + 19.4.\x*.
\v 17 Qiniso, N\nd kosi\nd*, amakhosi eAsiriya azichithile izizwe lelizwe lazo,
\v 18 aphosela onkulunkulu bazo emlilweni; ngoba babengeyisibo onkulunkulu, kodwa umsebenzi wezandla zabantu, izigodo lamatshe; ngakho bababhubhisa\x + Hlab. 115.4. 2 Lan. 32.19.\x*.
\v 19 Ngakho-ke, N\nd kosi\nd* Nkulunkulu wethu, ngicela usisindise esandleni sakhe, ukuze yonke imibuso yomhlaba yazi ukuthi wena uyiN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu, wena wedwa\x + Josh. 4.24.\x*.
\p
\v 20 UIsaya indodana kaAmozi wasethumela kuHezekhiya esithi: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu wakoIsrayeli: Lokho okukhuleke kimi mayelana loSenakheribi inkosi yeAsiriya ngikuzwile\x + 20.5.\x*.
\v 21 Yileli ilizwi iN\nd kosi\nd* elikhulume mayelana laye: Intombi emsulwa, indodakazi yeZiyoni, iyakudelela, iyakuklolodela\x + Lilo 2.13.\x*; indodakazi yeJerusalema inikina ikhanda ngemva kwakho\x + Jobe 16.4. Hlab. 22.7. 109.25. Lilo 2.15.\x*.
\v 22 Ngubani omeyisileyo\x + 19.4.\x* wamhlambaza\x + 19.6.\x*? Njalo uphakamisele bani ilizwi, waphakamisela amehlo akho phezulu? Umelene loNgcwele kaIsrayeli\x + Hlab. 71.22. Isa. 5.24. 60.9. Jer. 51.5.\x*.
\v 23 Ngesandla sezithunywa zakho uyeyisile iNkosi\x + 18.17.\x*, wathi: Ngobunengi bezinqola zami ngenyuke indawo ephezulu yezintaba\x + Hlab. 20.7.\x*, inhlangothi zeLebhanoni\x + Jer. 22.6,23. Hlu. 9.15.\x*. Ngizagamula imisedari yayo emide, \add l\add*amafiri ayo akhethekileyo\x + Jer. 22.6,23. Hlu. 9.15.\x*. Ngizangena endaweni yokuhlala yamaphethelo ayo, igusu eliminyeneyo\x + Josh. 19.26.\x*.
\v 24 Mina ngagebha nganatha amanzi angaziwayo, langengaphansi yenyawo zami ngomisa yonke imifula yezindawo ezivinjelweyo.
\v 25 Kawuzwanga yini ukuthi ngakwenza endulo\x + Isa. 45.7.\x*, ngakubumba ensukwini zendulo. Khathesi ngikufikisile, ukuthi ube ngowokudiliza imizi evikelweyo ibe zinqumbi zamanxiwa\x + Isa. 10.5.\x*.
\v 26 Ngakho abahlali bayo babelesandla esifitshane, besaba babe lenhloni, baba \add njengo\add*tshani beganga lemibhida eluhlaza\x + Gen. 1.11.\x*, utshani bempahla, lamabele ahanguliweyo engakami\x + Hlab. 129.6.\x*.
\v 27 Kodwa ngiyakwazi ukuhlala kwakho lokuphuma kwakho lokungena kwakho lokungithukuthelela kwakho\x + 1 Sam. 29.6.\x*.
\v 28 Ngenxa yokungithukuthelela kwakho, lokuthi umsindo wakho wenyukele endlebeni zami, ngizafaka umkhala wami emakhaleni akho, letomu lami endebeni zakho\x + Jobe 41.2. Isa. 30.28. Hez. 29.4. 38.4. Amos 4.2.\x*, ngikwenze ubuyele ngendlela oweza ngayo\x + 19.33,36.\x*.
\p
\v 29 Lokhu-ke kuzakuba yisibonakaliso kuwe\x + 20.8,9. 1 Sam. 2.34. Isa. 7.11,14. Luka 2.12. 1 Kho. 13.3.\x*; lonyaka uzakudla okuzikhulelayo\x + Levi 25.5,11. Levi 25.21,22.\x*, langomnyaka wesibili umkhukhuzela, kuthi ngomnyaka wesithathu lihlanyele livune, lihlanyele izivini lidle izithelo zazo.
\v 30 Lokuphephileyo kwendlu yakoJuda\x + 2 Lan. 32.22,23.\x* okuseleyo kuzaphinda kugxumeke impande phansi, kuthele izithelo ngaphezulu.
\v 31 Ngoba kuzaphuma eJerusalema insali, lokuphephileyo entabeni yeZiyoni. Ukutshiseka kweN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla kuzakwenza lokhu\x + Isa. 9.7.\x*.
\v 32 Ngakho utsho njalo uJehova ngenkosi yeAsiriya: Kayiyikungena kulumuzi, kayiyikutshoka umtshoko khona, kayiyikuza phambi kwawo \add ile\add*sihlangu, kayiyikubuthelela idundulu maqondana lawo\x + 2 Sam. 20.15.\x*.
\v 33 Ngendlela eyeza ngayo, ngayo izabuyela\x + 19.28.\x*, kayiyikungena kulo umuzi, itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 34 Ngoba ngizawuvikela lumuzi ukuwusindisa\x + 20.6. Isa. 31.5.\x*, ngenxa yami, langenxa kaDavida inceku yami\x + 1 Kho. 11.13.\x*.
\p
\v 35 Kwasekusithi ngalobobusuku\x + 2 Lan. 32.21. Hos. 1.7.\x* ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd* yaphuma\x + 2 Sam. 24.16.\x* yatshaya enkambeni yamaAsiriya izinkulungwane ezilikhulu lamatshumi ayisificaminwembili lanhlanu. Lapho bevuka ekuseni kakhulu, khangela, bonke babeyizidumbu ezifileyo\x + 19.8.\x*.
\v 36 Ngakho uSenakheribi inkosi yeAsiriya wasuka wahamba wabuyela, wahlala eNineve\x + Gen. 10.11. Jona 1.2.\x*.
\v 37 Kwasekusithi ekhonza endlini kaNisiroki unkulunkulu wakhe, oAdrameleki loSharezeri\x + 17.31.\x* amadodana akhe bamtshaya ngenkemba, bona baphephela elizweni leArarathi\x + 19.7.\x*. UEsarihadoni indodana yakhe wasebusa esikhundleni sakhe\x + Ezra 4.2.\x*.